                  <summary>Gospel of John, ወንጌል፡ ዘዮሐንስ፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="98v" facs="003">Fols 1r–98v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1693John">Gospel of John</title>
